    "The utilization of A utilizes the utilization of B2C marketers to make well-informed decisions and sustain a competitive advantage within the ever-changing social media environment (Sharma, Grewal & Kumar, 2023).",
    "Figure 3 The utilization of artificial intelligence (AI) in business-to-consumer (B2C) digital marketing",
